#### Keyboard shortcuts ####
" open new terminal split:
" 	:vert term
" 
" swap panes:
" 	ctrl+w, ctrl+r
"
" change width of pane:
" 	size, ctrl+w, |
" 	e.g. 300 ctrl+w, |
" open file in project path if you know the name but not the path:
" 	:find filename
" 	e.g. :find settings.py
